  "title": "Lorry Driver",
  "description": "<p>Roles & Responsibilities</p><p>~Class 3 Lorry Driver</p><p>~Delivery, loading and unloading of equipment and/or goods as designated</p><p>~Responsible to deliver operations materials to worksites</p><p>~Carry out daily checks to ensure vehicle’s road worthiness before use & maintain vehicle in clean condition.</p><p>~Material Shifting</p><p>~Report any faults and defects to supervisor immediately.</p><p>~Ensure safe lifting operations at all time and no overriding of safety devices.</p><p>~Comply with LTA Road Safety and traffic regulation and site safety related issue/ regulations</p><p>~Conduct preventive maintenance check and carry out maintenance and servicing when required.</p><p>~Adhere to statutory / company’s safety and health policies, procedures and regulations.</p><p>~Able to perform earthwork disposal</p><p>~Willing to work OT if required</p><p>~Able to handle physical work and with positive attitude</p><p>~Any other duties that may be assigned.</p>",
